# 💫 About Me:
## Tahreema Saleem<br>**Machine Learning Engineer | Deep Learning Practitioner**<br><br>I design, train, and evaluate machine learning and deep learning models for real-world applications across computer vision, speech, and natural language processing.<br><br>**Core Competencies:**<br><br>**Machine Learning**<br>- Supervised and unsupervised learning<br>- Regression and classification pipelines<br>- Model evaluation, validation, and hyperparameter tuning<br>- Scikit-learn, Pandas, NumPy<br><br>**Deep Learning**<br>- Neural network architectures from scratch<br>- Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for image analysis<br>- Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) and LSTMs for sequence data<br>- Transfer learning and fine-tuning pretrained models<br>- TensorFlow and Keras for model development<br><br>**Specialized Domains**<br>- Medical image analysis using CNNs<br>- Speech AI with Whisper and HuBERT<br>- Natural language processing for conversational AI<br>- Predictive modeling for healthcare and finance  <br><br>**What I'm focused on now:**<br>Taking models from development to production. Building reliable, scalable ML systems.<br><br>Open to deep learning roles and challenging problems.


